data.description: Quiet country living. This beautiful well maintained open concept manufactured home sits on 12 acres of east Texas tranquility. Features include 2 living spaces, a butler's pantry separating dining room from kitchen, huge primary bedroom and ensuite, large walk-in closet, spacious 2nd bathroom.  The home comes with all appliances, including washer and dryer, Samsung wifi connect fridge and extra overflow refrigerator. Tons of storage in the kitchen and walk-in pantry. Freshly painted. The winding driveway provides privacy from passer byers and 12 acres ensures the quietness of country living. Only 12 miles from Jasper and only 25 miles to Toledo Bend Dam.
